LogicalTable.name: Fact - CRM - Campaign History
LogicalTable.Description: This Fact enables analysis of Camapaign Execution facts by Account, Contact, Load, Wave, Marketing Source, Marketing Region, Time, Segment, Offer, Vendor, Call Status and EMail Bounce Types and reasons

LogicalColumn.Description: # of Campaigns
